{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"current","mdn_url":"/fr/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/current","locale":"fr","native":"Français","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">Référence XSLT/XPath</a></b> : <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">Éléments XSLT</a>, <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/EXSLT\">Fonctions EXSLT</a>, <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">Fonctions XPath</a>, <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">Axes XPath</a>\n</div>\n<p>La fonction <code>current</code> peut être utilisée pour obtenir le nœud courant dans une instruction XSLT.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntaxe","title":"Syntaxe","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">current()\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"retour","title":"Retour","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Un ensemble de nœuds contenant uniquement le nœud courant.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Notes","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Cette fonction est un ajout à XPath spécifique à XSLT. Elle ne fait pas partie de la bibliothèque de fonctions XPath core.</p>\n<p>Le nœud courant est toujours identique au nœud de contexte. Les deux exemples suivants sont sémantiquement équivalents&nbsp;:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token namespace\">xsl:</span>value-of</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">select</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>current()<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token namespace\">xsl:</span>value-of</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">select</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>.<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"définition","title":"Définition","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xslt#function-current\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">XSLT 1.0, section 12.4</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"support_gecko","title":"Support Gecko","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Supportée.</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"La fonction current peut être utilisée pour obtenir le nœud courant dans une instruction XSLT.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"current","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"current","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"current","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"fr/web/xpath/functions/current","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/fr/web/xpath/functions/current/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web","title":"Technologies web pour développeurs"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/XPath","title":"XPath"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/XPath/Functions","title":"Fonctions"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/current","title":"current"}],"pageTitle":"current - XPath | MDN","noIndexing":false}}